<?xml version="1.0" ?>
<gnn_model name="Factor Graph Active Inference Model" version="1.0">
  <metadata>
    <annotation>A factor graph decomposition of an Active Inference generative model with:
- Two independent observation modalities (visual and proprioceptive)
- Two independent hidden state factors (position and velocity)
- Factored joint distribution: P(o,s) = P(o_vis|s_pos) * P(o_prop|s_vel) * P(s_pos|s_vel) * P(s_vel)
- Variable nodes: observation and state variables
- Factor nodes: likelihood and transition factors
- Enables modality-specific processing and efficient belief propagation</annotation>
    <created_at>2026-03-17T16:46:47.817132</created_at>
    <modified_at>2026-03-17T16:46:47.817133</modified_at>
  </metadata>
  <variables>
